Detailed Description

Hysteresis end setting.

Sets the hysteresis end value after a number of decrements. Decrement interval time is controlled by axis parameter 164. -3... -1 negative hysteresis end setting 0 zero hysteresis end setting 1... 12 positive hysteresis end setting
